“Can we us AI tools help with our project” asked one of my grad students.

I encourage it. By using AI tools students learn how to leverage resources available to them, to adopt new solutions in a changing world, and where these solutions have limitations.

Students have realized ChatGPT doesn’t know everything, it makes mistakes, and is part of getting work but needs to be checked.  This is preparing them for the workforce in a realistic way. If I didn’t allow it, I’d be depriving them of learning.
